body:

Submissions to the EU Open Research Repository are automatically checked against the open science requirements in Horizon Europe. To learn more about the open science requirements please see:

- [Open Science in Horizon Europe](https://zenodo.org/communities/eu/pages/open-science)

The metadata checks are either:
- **required** - you must fix the error in order to publish/submit for review.
- **recommended** - you can publish/submit for review without fixing the recommendation.

The guide covers the following:

